Version pinning.  I don&#x27;t want a package manager, but I <i>do</i> want to be able to say<p><pre><code>    import (
        &quot;github.com/frio/mycoollibrary@1.2&quot;
    )
</code></pre>
... or some such (where the tag above could be a plain old hash too).<p>Vendoring in every library I use is not a great solution.
